msgstr "VoxCPM 2：48 kHz"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:106 c7988d6d4a204010ac2fecdbab6f14e9
msgid ""
"**Duration:** 3–30 seconds per clip is the practical sweet spot. Very short "
"clips (< 1s) produce unstable results. Very long clips increase VRAM usage "
"and may be filtered out by ``max_batch_tokens``."
msgstr ""
"**时长：** 每条片段 3–30 秒较为稳妥。过短（< 1 s）容易不稳定；过长会增加显存占用，并可能被 ``max_batch_tokens`` "
"过滤。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:109 abc60e9ac29e44319ef97c65c4ec05c3
msgid "Preprocessing tips"
msgstr "预处理建议"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:111 6aabf98981d540909a6c1e2ab08feee0
msgid ""
"**Trim trailing silence** to < 0.5 seconds. Long trailing silence is one of "
"the most common causes of \"generation doesn't stop\" after fine-tuning."
msgstr "**去掉尾部静音**，控制在 0.5 秒以内。尾静音过长是微调后「生成停不下来」最常见原因之一。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:112 9b1198035a9b4a97928ad4391556beb2
msgid "**Normalize volume** if your recordings have inconsistent levels."
msgstr "若录音电平不一致，**请做音量归一化**。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:113 f839bf4688aa4e3a9ad6dd38512c579e
msgid ""
"**Clean transcripts:** Ensure the text matches the audio exactly. Mismatched"
" text degrades both cloning quality and text adherence."
msgstr "**转写要干净：** 文本须与音频逐字一致；不匹配会同时损害克隆质量与文本贴合度。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:114 b59139c777aa48dd9d712fcf9787a2c3
msgid ""
"**Remove noisy samples.** The model is sensitive to background noise in "
"training data."
msgstr "**剔除噪声样本。** 模型对训练数据中的背景噪声较敏感。"

