#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:251 f032aab856c7471ca2890c51fdb3c761
msgid "Training logs to TensorBoard. Start the viewer with:"
msgstr "训练日志写入 TensorBoard。可用如下命令启动查看："

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:257 c67af5bbceec43bfa60e2ef0e75cd212
msgid "**What to watch**"
msgstr "**关注哪些指标**"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:263 67cdc2d9adb64e7696765925c5c5e5b2
msgid "Metric"
msgstr "指标"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:264 b07a21892ac84e6ba7a974b0cfa70073
msgid "What it tells you"
msgstr "含义"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:265 0099ef11363942be83660b89ba24d22c
msgid "``loss/diff``"
msgstr "``loss/diff``"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:266 290f7f843dc34c03a02660c14176223f
msgid "Diffusion loss — should steadily decrease, then flatten"
msgstr "扩散损失 — 应持续下降后趋于平稳"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:267 9fb4dbc50c6f4332aaaa6c2c63b0da5d
msgid "``loss/stop``"
msgstr "``loss/stop``"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:268 1114f432d6d44495a49dc45998c10c19
msgid "Stop prediction loss — should stabilize early and stay low"
msgstr "停止预测损失 — 应较早稳定并保持较低"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:269 8d1856487b6e4ec79d662bfaaa17ba34
msgid "``grad_norm``"
msgstr "``grad_norm``"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:270 efad2a7f6771425494b1ac9c66830dad
msgid ""
"Gradient magnitude — spikes may indicate bad samples or too high a learning "
"rate"
msgstr "梯度范数 — 尖峰可能表示坏样本或学习率过高"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:271 a44d1b0be32e42eaa85634c56940496b
msgid "``lr``"
msgstr "``lr``"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:272 af92cc0dd4ee443187d48b6a53e0d20b
msgid ""
"Learning rate curve — cosine decay with warmup, useful to verify your "
"schedule"
msgstr "学习率曲线 — 带 warm-up 的余弦衰减，可用于核对调度是否符合预期"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:274 cc6c58cb683648d6ade37e8898dfc663
msgid ""
"If a validation manifest is provided, the script also logs ``val/loss`` and "
"generates sample audio + mel spectrograms in TensorBoard at each "
"``valid_interval``."
msgstr ""
"若提供验证清单，脚本还会记录 ``val/loss``，并在每个 `` valid_interval`` 在 TensorBoard 中生成样本音频与 "
"mel 频谱。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:276 250603bdf6784a13bf400b76c17dc118
msgid "**When to stop**"
msgstr "**何时停止**"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:278 1670c57628b4496eab0ab26d07adae3e
msgid ""
"**Use epochs as a rough guide.** For single-speaker cloning, 1–3 epochs are "
"usually sufficient. Going beyond that often hurts rather than helps — "
"overfitting in TTS fine-tuning can emerge very early."
msgstr ""
"**可把 epoch 数当作粗参考。** 单说话人克隆通常 1–3 个 epoch 足够；再往后往往弊大于利 — TTS 微调的过拟合可能很早出现。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:279 955ebb6bbfc6436980c81f2a3f40ce8a
msgid "``loss/diff`` plateaus and no longer decreases meaningfully."
msgstr "``loss/diff`` 进入平台期，不再有实质下降。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:280 ffca585c61b64635be36206e084117d0
msgid "Generated audio in TensorBoard sounds good on your target voice/style."
msgstr "TensorBoard 中的生成音频在目标音色/风格上听起来已经满意。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:281 54bee2b706394f8f9c27ffe06b951275
msgid ""
"If the model starts ignoring input text (generating the same audio "
"regardless of text), you have overfit — roll back to an earlier checkpoint."
msgstr "若模型开始忽略输入文本（无论输入什么都生成相似音频），即已过拟合 — 请回退到较早的 checkpoint。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:285 ca52326b9f9940b6b83588740e359749
msgid ""
"Validation loss does not always correlate perfectly with perceptual quality."
" Save multiple checkpoints around the convergence zone and evaluate them "
"with actual inference to pick the best one."
msgstr "验证损失与主观听感未必完全一致。建议在收敛区间附近多存几个 checkpoint，用实际推理试听后再选定最佳。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:287 ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:425
#: 61a7314277bc4e34b375a353c738c282 b849ff856445467381854c40f73affc6
msgid "**Checkpoint structure**"
msgstr "**Checkpoint 目录结构**"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:302 1b948a8a77c7493eaa061cc897814efe
msgid ""
"Training automatically resumes from ``latest/`` if it exists. The signal "
"handler also saves a checkpoint on ``SIGTERM`` / ``SIGINT`` so you don't "
"lose progress on interruption."
msgstr ""
"若存在 ``latest/``，训练会自动从中恢复；信号处理也会在 `` SIGTERM`` / `` SIGINT`` 时保存 "
"checkpoint，避免中断丢进度。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:305 ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:445
#: 2cc4b4da5d3042d19b1351c9b80bfa9f 96fe84b7510941268b5818de50e446b2
msgid "Inference"
msgstr "推理"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:307 ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:447
#: 4ad32c92013847f8a8a04acaa9ad48aa 6b20233d4f5a4b71824484a26215d5ed
msgid "**CLI**"
msgstr "**命令行**"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:317 ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:464
#: 37d17d04df8b438087300b78c4bd9a8d 7987ceb9cf15415bab60fe2dd6636a9a
msgid "**Python API**"
msgstr "**Python API**"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:330 1393f1669326454caddc2b3017fb7a61
msgid "**Hot-swapping LoRA at runtime**"
msgstr "**运行时热切换 LoRA**"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:332 5e3b667d5bef44d986e726d35e8b5849
msgid ""
"You can load, unload, and switch LoRA weights without restarting the model:"
msgstr "无需重启模型即可加载、卸载或切换 LoRA 权重："

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:349 7eabbe4b5f874b1eb1cc99acd31a3875
msgid "All hot-swap operations are compatible with ``torch.compile``."
msgstr "所有热切换操作均与 ``torch.compile`` 兼容。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:358 d35953cb90cc4827aef54437d3890790
msgid ""
"Full fine-tuning updates all model parameters. Use it when LoRA does not "
"provide enough capacity — typically for new languages or large-scale "
"customization with 500+ clips."
msgstr "全量微调会更新全部参数。当 LoRA 容量不足时使用 — 常见于新语言或 500+ 条片段的大规模定制。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:393 7529e315ff134f75b4906bcc73f92a9f
msgid ""
"Note the ``lora`` key is absent — this tells the script to do full fine-"
"tuning."
msgstr "注意配置中不含 ``lora`` 键 — 脚本据此执行全量微调。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:395 b7da6f59b2ea4d838bcd66892cb567e1
msgid "**Key differences from LoRA**"
msgstr "**与 LoRA 的主要区别**"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:397 51035738a9754d9d8e50283b944c2838
msgid ""
"``learning_rate`` should be ~10x smaller (``1e-5`` vs ``1e-4``) to avoid "
"catastrophic forgetting."
msgstr "``learning_rate`` 建议约为 LoRA 的 1/10（`` 1e-5`` 对 `` 1e-4``），以避免灾难性遗忘。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:398 c510885d18e846b69e525fe4caa1f0b3
msgid ""
"VRAM usage is significantly higher because all parameters require gradients."
msgstr "因全部参数都参与求导，显存占用明显更高。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:399 b6230bc1887e4846a46e5d351cd4be4b
msgid "Checkpoints are larger (full model weights vs. LoRA delta only)."
msgstr "checkpoint 更大（完整权重对比仅 LoRA 增量）。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:415 3f6a126b8bd648feb6474d0616313ec5
msgid ""
"Same TensorBoard metrics as LoRA (``loss/diff``, ``loss/stop``, "
"``grad_norm``, ``lr``, validation audio)."
msgstr ""
"TensorBoard 指标与 LoRA 相同（``loss/diff``、`` loss/stop``、`` grad_norm``、`` lr`` "
"及验证音频）。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:417 69f7b3dc7d5f48c2aa021e01a062fa33
msgid ""
"Full fine-tuning is more prone to overfitting than LoRA. In practice, full "
"fine-tuning often reaches its optimum within 1–2 epochs — continuing beyond "
"that can degrade quality. Pay extra attention to:"
msgstr "全量微调比 LoRA 更易过拟合。实践中常在 1–2 个 epoch 内达到较优；继续训练可能反而变差。需格外留意："

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:419 d900511939024af091cba4a6b972e520
msgid ""
"**Validation loss diverging from training loss** — a sign of overfitting. "
"Stop and use the last checkpoint before divergence."
msgstr "**验证损失与训练损失背离** — 过拟合信号。应停止训练，并采用背离前最后一个 checkpoint。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:420 c8db0267e4ab425eb3b87c4eca1d8c03
msgid ""
"**Text being ignored** — the most common overfitting symptom. Keep "
"``training_cfg_rate=0.1`` (do not set it to 0) and ``weight_decay=0.01``. "
"Monitor checkpoints at each ``save_interval``."
msgstr ""
"**文本被忽略** — 最常见的过拟合表现。请保持 ``training_cfg_rate=0.1`` （不要设为 0）与 `` "
"weight_decay=0.01``，并在每个 `` save_interval`` 关注 checkpoint。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:421 6ef255c0d64547d0aaa58ce281289541
msgid ""
"**Smaller datasets overfit faster.** With fewer training samples, the "
"optimal checkpoint may appear within a few hundred steps."
msgstr "**小数据集更快过拟合。** 样本较少时，最优 checkpoint 可能出现在几百步内。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:422 6e99e558e73249cfbe5df8eefae80fbb
msgid ""
"**New language fine-tuning:** Mix in some Chinese/English data (e.g. 10–20%)"
" to reduce forgetting of the original capabilities."
msgstr "**新语言微调：** 混入部分中英数据（例如 10–20%），以减轻对原有能力的遗忘。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:423 467c44076243487aa02217355ad176f0
msgid ""
"**More data does not always mean better results.** Beyond a certain point, "
"adding more data yields diminishing returns; focus on data quality and "
"diversity instead."
msgstr "**更多数据未必更好。** 超过某一点后边际收益递减；更应重视数据质量与多样性。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:442 a65723dd0c4943e6b84d644dda53fbe4
msgid ""
"Each checkpoint is a complete model directory that can be loaded directly."
msgstr "每个 checkpoint 都是可直接加载的完整模型目录。"

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:466 403b9a28c54941a8bd98ecec4283a6ee
msgid "The checkpoint directory is a complete model — load it directly:"
msgstr "该目录即完整模型 — 可直接加载："

#: ../../finetuning/finetune.rst:477 f704186bf19e471da84415b077c52d66
msgid ""
"For common training issues (OOM, runaway generation, poor LoRA performance, "
"checkpoint errors), see :doc:`./faq`."
msgstr "常见训练问题（OOM、生成停不下来、LoRA 效果差、checkpoint 报错等）请参阅 :doc:`./faq`。"
